divs: Sighting DetailsI walked onto my balcony, saw a white object approaching. I had seen this object in the past speeding eratically acros the sky. I grabbed my camera and saw it morph into a plane. I took two images on my digital camera before it went behind the trees. When I looked at my camera, I noticed that my dates and settings had changed, even on the image properties. www.ascensionfiles.com.
Summary: White object morphs into unmarked white airplane.
